<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:50:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>泰国相信援助努力将引发缅甸危机对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-confident-aid-effort-will-lead-myanmar-crisis-dialogue-2024-02-06/</link><description>泰国一名高级官员表示，泰国领导的一项新的人道主义倡议旨在为军事统治的缅甸交战阵营之间的谈判铺平道路，三年前，一场政变引发了全国各地的不稳定和暴力浪潮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-confident-aid-effort-will-lead-myanmar-crisis-dialogue-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>总理称中国法院对澳大利亚作家缓刑的判决“令人愤慨”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-courts-suspended-death-sentence-australian-writer-an-outrage-pm-says-2024-02-05/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞周二表示，北京法院以间谍罪判处澳大利亚作家杨恒均死刑缓期执行，这“令人愤慨”，并誓言将继续努力争取杨恒均获释。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-courts-suspended-death-sentence-australian-writer-an-outrage-pm-says-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部团队本周前往中国讨论补贴和经济政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-treasury-team-heads-china-this-week-talk-subsidies-economic-policies-2024-02-05/</link><description>一位财政部官员周一表示，拜登政府本周将派遣五名美国财政部高级官员前往北京进行经济会谈，会谈将重点关注中国增加工业产能过剩的“非市场”政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-treasury-team-heads-china-this-week-talk-subsidies-economic-policies-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：澳洲联储关注美国债券收益率飙升蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>Stake F1车队以双重身份规避赌博限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/stake-f1-team-swerves-gambling-restrictions-with-dual-identity-2024-02-05/</link><description>索伯运营的 Stake 一级方程式车队本赛季将以两个名字参加比赛，以遵守一些国家的赌博限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 20:26:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/stake-f1-team-swerves-gambling-restrictions-with-dual-identity-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟警告不要采取支持太阳能行业的贸易措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cautions-against-trade-measures-support-solar-sector-2024-02-05/</link><description>欧盟一位高级官员周一表示，在考虑采取任何措施限制光伏电池板、硅片和其他零部件进口之前，欧盟需要考虑其雄心勃勃的太阳能部署目标。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 19:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cautions-against-trade-measures-support-solar-sector-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院共和党人考虑边境协议，众议院同行敦促拒绝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/republican-us-senate-border-negotiator-says-party-should-decide-next-move-by-2024-02-05/</link><description>美国参议院两党加强边境安全法案的首席共和党谈判代表表示，他的核心小组应在周二之前决定是否就该提案展开辩论，而众议院共和党领导人则敦促废除该协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 19:07:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/republican-us-senate-border-negotiator-says-party-should-decide-next-move-by-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国瞄准保证金贷款和卖空以帮助稳定股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-targets-margin-loans-short-selling-help-stabilise-stocks-2024-02-05/</link><description>中国证监会周一表示，将加强对融资融券、恶意卖空行为的监管，防范质押股票风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:15:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-targets-margin-loans-short-selling-help-stabilise-stocks-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>分析师预计稀土价格将在 2024 年下半年反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rare-earths-prices-seen-rebounding-second-half-2024-analysts-2024-02-05/</link><description>分析师表示，稀土价格可能已经触底，并有望在今年晚些时候上涨，因为电动汽车和风电的需求以及主要生产国中国预计将取消扩大的产量配额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:55:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rare-earths-prices-seen-rebounding-second-half-2024-analysts-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>工作忧虑让中国人回家度假心情不好</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/job-worries-sour-mood-chinese-heading-home-holidays-2024-02-05/</link><description>周一，中国工人们挤上火车回家过农历新年假期，他们对工作和经济不景气的担忧给人们期待已久的家庭团聚蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:31:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/job-worries-sour-mood-chinese-heading-home-holidays-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>杨恒均：这句话对中澳关系意味着什么</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-harsh-sentence-australian-writer-tests-limits-rebound-ties-2024-02-05/</link><description>分析人士表示，澳大利亚作家杨恒均周一在北京被判处死刑缓期执行，这不太可能破坏澳中关系，但将考验堪培拉在多年紧张关系后推动两国关系重回正轨的努力的极限。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-harsh-sentence-australian-writer-tests-limits-rebound-ties-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：随着股市暴跌，中国券商限制跨境互换--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-brokers-restrict-cross-border-swaps-stocks-plunge-sources-2024-02-05/</link><description>据六位知情人士透露，为了捍卫疲软的股市，包括国有巨头中国国际金融公司（中金公司）在内的中国券商限制了国内投资者可以进行的跨境掉期交易金额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-brokers-restrict-cross-border-swaps-stocks-plunge-sources-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚人杨恒均在中国被判处死刑缓期执行，他是一位富有魅力的博主、间谍小说家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/yang-hengjun-australian-given-suspended-death-sentence-china-was-charismatic-2024-02-05/</link><description>澳大利亚博主杨恒均周一在北京一家法院出庭，因间谍罪名被判处死刑缓期执行，他在悉尼的朋友说，他看起来“非常瘦弱，非常脆弱”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/yang-hengjun-australian-given-suspended-death-sentence-china-was-charismatic-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>雅诗兰黛因中国需求不稳定而裁员；股价飙升19%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-slashes-annual-profit-forecast-cut-jobs-2024-02-05/</link><description>雅诗兰黛计划在全球裁员 3% 至 5%，因为这家化妆品巨头加大了努力，以支撑因中国客户削减高价奢侈品而受到挤压的利润率，导致其股价上涨高达 19%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 11:49:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-slashes-annual-profit-forecast-cut-jobs-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：AI芯片需求迫使华为放缓智能手机生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ai-chip-demand-forces-huawei-slow-smartphone-production-sources-2024-02-05/</link><description>对华为人工智能芯片的需求飙升，加上制造限制，迫使这家中国科技巨头优先考虑人工智能，并放慢了其高端 Mate 60 手机的生产速度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/ai-chip-demand-forces-huawei-slow-smartphone-production-sources-2024-02-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>